    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no actual \"rest\" in this life. like even if i stop fighting, i'm still just here, still stuck in this body and this skin, still facing everyone's judgment. when you say \"let go of the fight entirely,\" it almost sounds like you're saying it's okay to just... stop being. like it's a valid option.",
